 itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the co-founder=
 replied</a>, =E2=80=9CI give the question back: What is reality?=E2=80=9D =
Always the relevant question in this business.</p>
