<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He continued: =E2=80=9CThis adds another produ=
ct to the life cycle. It may elongate the life cycle. But it adds another p=
roduct.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Honestly a longer life cycle is better, if you=
